text: Nürtingen (German: ['nirdeŋɐ]; ; Swabian: Nirdeng ['ni:rdeŋ]; High German: Nirdenga) is a town on the Neckar. It is in Esslingen, a district (Landkreis) in Baden-Württemberg in southern Germany. == References == == Other websites == * Official Website * Official Website of University (German & English) Category:Towns in Baden-Württemberg Category:Esslingen (district) Category:Württemberg
